This paper deals with the relationship between causal models and counterfactual structures, which are important concepts in artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves mathematical analysis and comparisons between different models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CE (computational engineering), cs.IT (information theory), or cs.DS (data structures and algorithms).
